						<summary>

						<p>Pāṇḍya, Vīrapāṇḍya, 9th year = c. 13 Century.</p>						

						<p>This records a gift of land to the temple of Tiruvaraṅguḷam-uḍaiya-nāyaṉār, perhaps by the same person mentioned in the above inscription (No. 257).</p>						

