<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tiripuvaṉa cakkaravat
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tikaḷ civīrapāṇṭiya tēva<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku yā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇṭu Oṉpatāvatu Uṭaiyār tiruvaraṅ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kuḷamuṭaiya nāyaṉāṟku tirunāmattu
<lb n="5"/>kāṇiyāka koṇṭa cōmaṉ kuḻi Uḷḷa Ū
<lb n="6" break="no"/>r Uḷpaṭṭa nāṉ kellaiyilum Eḻuntaruḷuvi
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>vi</unclear>tta tiruccūla tēvakaḷukkuḷppaṭṭa nīr nilaṅkaḷu
<lb n="8"/>m puṉcai maraṅkaḷu kālukkum perunaṟki<supplied reason="omitted">ḷ</supplied>ḷic cō
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ḻa nāṭāḻvār kuṭikkāṭu nāṉkellaikkuḷ paṭṭa ni
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="9" unit="character"/> It tirukkoḷkai <unclear>veḷḷi</unclear>yum
<lb n="11"/>mēl pāricattil kalveṭṭiṉa tirumēka
<lb n="12" break="no"/>laiyum kalveṭṭi paṭṭayam Inta nilaṅka
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ḷ tirunāmattukāṇiyāka koṇṭatu 
